Nerdgasm (also known as nerd-gasm)

In the recent populatity of "[[Sex in the City]]"'s tendency to put the suffix "-gasm" with a word, place, or activity that is exciting, [[nerds]] have placed the word "-gasm" with nerd. This word means something that would excite a [[nerd]], [[geek]], or [[fanboy]]. And example of this would be the announcing of a release date for a new [[video game console]], or a new scientific discovery.